Name: Eat Me Alive
About the game: You are the bug! You decide the best body part to settle into. Create offspring and keep evolving into a better self. But be aware of your human host, you do not want to upset or even kill it. ▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬●▬ The goal of the game is to find a good balance between getting your ressources without upsetting the host. You can place yourself on any body part to get different ressources. Also by researching different genetic evolutions you can place bugs with distinct features.
